{"tid":1242921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天主教基督教聲明促撤修例　獨立調查612警民衝突","createTime":"2019-06-19T08:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T15:55:03.000Z","uid":2617,"like":127,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"46ca1d9de8e00105e0a874cf18c9cc12fd02cacd","tid":1242921,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:55:59.000Z","msg":"宗教界再就修訂逃犯條例爭議發聲，天主教香港教區宗座署理湯漢樞機，以及香港基督教協進會主席蘇成溢牧師共同發出聲明，促請特區政府明確聲明「撤回法案」，獨立調查612 警民衝突。<br />\n<br />\n兩人透過新聞稿共同回應行政長官林鄭月娥，昨日在記者會就「修例」事件的交代。<br />\n<br />\n他們說，對行政長官向市民公開道歉，承認自己的不足，深表認同；又呼籲特區政府從速成立獨立委員會，徹查6.12警民衝突的真相，鑑往知來。<br />\n<br />\n他們認為，政府雖然已表明停止有關條例的立法程序，但仍呼籲政府考慮廣大市民的強烈要求，明確聲明「撤回法案」。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好彩有耶穌溫提大家未撤回<br />\nsing hallelujah to the lord</span></span>"},{"pid":"ec95ed0150a85937bc527807a2fac01efccbd5cf","tid":1242921,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938af037d9e5c823f1390ed01553b7fe516ba0eb","tid":1242921,"uid":154486,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"湯漢又轉軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00286e0ca2a09274bf8b031743d18d91cbda3395","tid":1242921,"uid":2617,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"938af037d9e5c823f1390ed01553b7fe516ba0eb","tid":1242921,"uid":154486,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"湯漢又轉軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:58:41.000Z","msg":"轉岩就ok<br />\n繼續比動力大家"},{"pid":"1c99be26c3ed671c20